==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sylphid
<hw>Sylph"id</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>sylphide</ets>, fem. See <er>Sylph</er>.]</ety> <def>A little
sylph; a young or diminutive sylph.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧The place of the
<xex>sylphid</xex> queen.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>J. R. Drake.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Ye sylphs and <qex>sylphids</qex>, to your chief give ear,⟦br⟧
Fays, fairies, genii, elves, and demons, hear.</q>
<rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sylphine</ent>⟦br⟧
